rows.label: qst200802_msg0001
rows.name:
What the hell? They ain't nothin' but
a bunch of women and children, and
they still kicked our butts...

rows.label: qst200802_msg0002
rows.name:
I'll remember you, ya stinkin' brats!
Don't think for a minute you'll get
away with this!

rows.label: qst200802_msg0004
rows.name:
Um, Hotaru. Are you sure you don't
know what those mercs wanted?

rows.label: qst200802_msg0005
rows.name:
Yes, positive.
I have no idea whatsoever.

rows.label: qst200802_msg0006
rows.name:
But Hotaru often receive gifts from
people, could maybe be one of those?

rows.label: qst200802_msg0007
rows.name:
Huh?
Sure, but I'd remember getting
top-secret information I think...
